summary: This is an email from Bulletin Intelligence to the FBI containing the Director's AM News Briefing for May 31, 2018. It appears to be routine internal FBI communication regarding daily news briefings and includes contractual restrictions on distribution.

events.title: FBI Director's AM News Briefing
events.description: Daily morning news briefing prepared for the FBI Director, distributed internally to FBI employees.

keyFacts: This document is an email distributing the FBI Director's AM News Briefing dated May 31, 2018.
The briefing is marked as copyrighted material for internal FBI use only and cannot be redistributed without express written consent.
The document shows routine internal FBI communication procedures for distributing news briefings to employees.
